Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.51,0:00:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.47,0:00:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.39,0:00:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.62,0:00:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:35.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:40.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:47.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:52.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.77,0:00:58.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever, I take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.46,0:01:06.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it’s not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:16.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:21.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard someone else’s biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.55,0:01:25.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn’t there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:30.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.83,0:01:36.31,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.33,0:01:42.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.59,0:01:48.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.27,0:01:52.83,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.85,0:01:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:01:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.71,0:02:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.82,0:02:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.21,0:02:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.33,0:02:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.39,0:02:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.37,0:02:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago, I made the decision\Nthat I'd never again build a ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.57,0:02:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wanted to catch up to the\Nperson who was my goal after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.88,0:02:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next thing I knew, I was\Ndrawing blueprints for a ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.32,0:02:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dream is... to use that treasure tree...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.38,0:02:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to build one last ship...\NA dream ship that crosses any sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.52,0:03:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already obtained this treasure tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.78,0:03:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already got blueprints, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.09,0:03:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to build this ship now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... when it's completed...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.14,0:03:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will you set sail on the ship I've built?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.78,0:03:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.89,0:03:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.40,0:03:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.42,0:03:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.17,0:03:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Ouch! That hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.92,0:03:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt?! What're you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a punch! There's no\Nway that'd work on rubber!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no means to ward off a fist of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.05,0:03:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you've gone on\Nquite the rampage, huh, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.56,0:04:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ack! G-G-G...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.60,0:04:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A Navy Vice Admiral is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.37,0:04:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Strongest Family?\NLuffy's Father Revealed!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.74,0:04:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.43,0:04:36.62,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there something you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:37.29,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,1)}"Monkey D. Garp\N'Garp the Fist'\NVice Admiral, Navy Headquarters"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.31,0:04:41.85,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,need to apologize to me for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.87,0:04:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Admiral Garp's got a grandson?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.89,0:04:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first I've heard of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Garp" is the name of a Navy hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.51,0:04:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Is he really your grandpa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.34,0:05:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Don't you dare mess with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was small, he almost\Nkilled me a bunch of times!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.56,0:05:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, don't go around giving me a bad name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shoved you into a bottomless pit...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I threw you into a jungle at night...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I attached you to balloons and let them fly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.44,0:05:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did all those things in order\Nto make you a strong man!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I've just discovered where\NLuffy's endless vitality comes from...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.38,0:06:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I eventually entrusted you with my\Nfriend and had you train with Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.49,0:06:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I take my eyes off you,\Nand look what happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I trained you to become a strong marine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.62,0:06:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you over and over that\NI wanted to become a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.33,0:06:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got corrupted by "Red Hair"! How foolish!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.67,0:06:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shanks saved my life! Don't badmouth him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.63,0:06:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you talk like that to your grandpa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.99,0:06:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.89,0:06:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible! Luffy got captured by the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.15,0:06:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.43,0:06:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me! Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Luffy's combative spirit against\Nthat old man has already been broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.36,0:06:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! They fell asleep?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.76,0:07:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, what the heck should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been in this kind of situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. I fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.23,0:07:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.96,0:07:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.39,0:07:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how you behave\Nwhen you're being scolded?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.63,0:07:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's not how you should speak\Nto your grandpa in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.24,0:07:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care anymore. Do as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.78,0:07:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Luffy's grandpa is a marine\Nat Navy Headquarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting crazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.33,0:07:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Th-That hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.59,0:07:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even know what kind of pirate\N"Red Hair" is to start with?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.32,0:08:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shanks?! Are they... Are Shanks\Nand the others doing okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.28,0:08:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.53,0:08:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.78,0:08:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there are countless pirates\Nnowadays, but out of all of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he's ranked in the top four pirates,\Nin the same league as Whitebeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.52,0:08:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These four reign over the second half\Nof the Grand Line like emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.84,0:08:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So people call them the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.22,0:08:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Navy Headquarters and the\NSeven Warlords of the Sea
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have joined together to\Nfight against these four!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the balance among these\Nthree great powers is lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.08,0:08:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it is said that world peace will fall apart.\NThat's how large their power is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Err...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.15,0:08:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't really get all that,\Nbut it's good to hear he's doing okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.30,0:08:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.83,0:08:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave this hat with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dear to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:09:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take good care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.11,0:09:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come bring it back to me someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you've become a great pirate!\NThat's our promise, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.94,0:09:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and "Red Hair" know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy told me that this guy\Nentrusted the straw hat with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.61,0:09:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't realize this guy\Nwas such a famous person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.54,0:09:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This way, Zoro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! The Navy is already here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.29,0:09:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.02,0:09:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry that we tried to extort you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, don't worry about it!\NThanks for showing me the way! Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:09:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Pirate Hunter Zoro,\Na criminal with a bounty on his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.67,0:10:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...? That's Luffy's friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's quite energetic, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you guys, try stopping him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.18,0:10:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.03,0:10:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kukris, huh? It's not often that you see those.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.36,0:10:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiya! Hiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.69,0:10:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Zoro, wait! You don't have to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...? You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.49,0:10:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shave!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.91,0:10:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This technique...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.13,0:10:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sergeant Major!\N--Sergeant!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are no match for them at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd expect no less from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:11:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I concede!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.50,0:11:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san! Zoro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while. Do you recognize me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.80,0:11:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.11,0:11:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me! Coby!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.89,0:11:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.50,0:11:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coby?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.08,0:11:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think... even I could join the Navy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.80,0:11:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Navy?\N--Yes! Catching bad guys is my dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.43,0:11:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been my dream ever since I was little!\NDo you think I can do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.66,0:11:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san and I haven't known\Neach other long, but we are friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.00,0:11:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We're gonna part ways,\Nbut we'll always be friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! I'll never forget\Nall you've done for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet again sometime, Coby!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.12,0:11:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy-san...\N--Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.67,0:11:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All hands, salute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.45,0:12:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.60,0:12:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coby?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.94,0:12:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do have a friend Coby...\Nbut the Coby I know was short.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's me! The Coby who\Nwas a hopeless crybaby!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.81,0:12:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Is that true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.31,0:12:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Coby?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you in the Grand Line?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've still got a ways to go\Nto become a Navy Officer,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.00,0:12:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but when I heard that you were nearby,\NI just wanted to see you guys so badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.36,0:12:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:32.80,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We owe you two for helping us
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.82,0:12:34.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,1)}"Coby\NSergeant Major, Navy Headquarters"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.16,0:12:36.89,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,become who we are now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.91,0:12:37.36,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,1)}"Helmeppo\NSergeant, Navy Headquarters"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.38,0:12:40.22,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I wouldn't go that far, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For various reasons, Vice Admiral Garp\Nis currently training us at Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.33,0:13:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, usually people can\Nonly grow so much, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.25,0:13:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your body was flabby!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for visiting now, when you're\Ntired after all you went through.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.58,0:13:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it. It's been\Na while. Let's have a party!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.89,0:13:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a sec, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.14,0:13:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't noticed me, have you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.34,0:13:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.89,0:13:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.41,0:13:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know you. Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.56,0:13:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Helmeppo. The son of Captain Morgan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.94,0:13:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helmeppo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.10,0:13:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the man who crucified you and\Nnearly executed you, Roronoa Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.54,0:13:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you remember me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.13,0:13:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.84,0:14:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.12,0:14:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not nice to be a bully!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.44,0:14:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem surprisingly well, Roronoa Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.30,0:14:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Take this! And this!\N--Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.69,0:14:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That specially treated stupid son!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.98,0:14:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.65,0:14:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah... There was a\Nguy like that. So it's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't stand these guys, Coby!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.32,0:14:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped, Helmeppo-san.\NYou should accept the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.91,0:14:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.04,0:14:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.01,0:14:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san, you and I are now enemies, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.18,0:14:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...are we still... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.42,0:14:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. We're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, you guys...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.94,0:15:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.51,0:15:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Repair this wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.51,0:15:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,0:15:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were going to have it fixed,\Nwhy did you break it in the first place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cooler to go in that way, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.12,0:15:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't break things for reasons like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, we'll repair it,\Nso please help us, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.56,0:15:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.64,0:15:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought your grandpa was a big shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I don't know much about his job.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.56,0:15:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.00,0:15:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you saw your old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.94,0:15:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! My dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.54,0:16:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by my dad? I have a dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.26,0:16:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Then he didn't tell you who he was?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that he saw you off at Loguetown.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.98,0:16:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Loguetown...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.30,0:16:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Err...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.73,0:16:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the island where Loguetown is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That island is where Gold Roger\Nwas born and then executed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.52,0:16:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you actually remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.71,0:16:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The town where the King of the Pirates died...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.58,0:16:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also known as the city\Nof the beginning and end...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.17,0:16:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:16:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To my several hundred billion\Nservants around the world! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.97,0:17:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll now super flashily\Nstart the open execution!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.23,0:17:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy! You can\Nno longer move even an inch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You feel honored, Straw Hat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.61,0:17:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can die in the same place\Nthe King of the Pirates died.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.82,0:17:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you have a big audience, do you\Nwanna say something before you die?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.99,0:17:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.29,0:17:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether you wanna say something or not\Ndoesn't matter, since you're gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.76,0:17:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the man who'll be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.74,0:17:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:18:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even Zoro can stop me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.20,0:18:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end of your captain!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.20,0:18:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.54,0:18:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I cut down the execution platform...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.38,0:18:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro! Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.88,0:18:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hurry up!\N--Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--This is heavy!\N--Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.15,0:18:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.32,0:18:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still alive after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.43,0:19:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.46,0:19:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hat gang is running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.68,0:19:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Capture them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.71,0:19:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go after them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.23,0:19:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy's old man was in that town?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.05,0:19:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's my dad like?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.69,0:19:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm curious... about Luffy's father!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.03,0:19:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father's name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Monkey D. Dragon. He's a revolutionary!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're running out of your devil's luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.87,0:19:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.93,0:19:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.74,0:19:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.69,0:20:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-T-The revolutionary Dragon has a son?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.38,0:20:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san is the son of that Dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... Dragon is Vice Admiral Garp's son?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.09,0:20:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is with his family?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.63,0:20:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard Dragon's full name before!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.41,0:20:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys... What are you so surprised about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.81,0:20:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! You don't know the name "Dragon"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.78,0:20:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father is a dangerous man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.72,0:20:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.10,0:20:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.40,0:20:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I explain it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.63,0:20:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates wouldn't start a fight\Nwith the Government or Navy,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.78,0:21:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there's a power trying to bring down\Nthe World Government directly now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.91,0:21:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the revolutionary army.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.79,0:21:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Dragon is the man who leads it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.76,0:21:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their ideology has now spread in\Nmany countries around the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.05,0:21:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which caused rebellions and\Nled several kingdoms to fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.44,0:21:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The government naturally became angry
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.16,0:21:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and has been searching everywhere for\Ntheir mastermind, Dragon, all this time
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.89,0:21:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as the world's most heinous criminal...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.09,0:21:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but he's been considered a mysterious man\Nwhose background was completely unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.13,0:21:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.39,0:21:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.58,0:21:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I shouldn't have said anything about it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.50,0:21:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,0:22:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.72,0:22:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...forget what I just said!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.02,0:22:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.23,0:22:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really going back already?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.63,0:22:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you have dinner with us? Dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.61,0:22:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're enemies. We can't become close, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.74,0:22:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad that I was able\Nto see you two again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.62,0:22:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet again for sure in the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.98,0:22:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.32,0:22:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Its Name Is the New World!\NThe Fate of the Grand Line!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.98,0:22:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
